4,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:18","price":"و به آسمان [نمی‌نگرند] که چگونه برافراشته شده است؟","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5985,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:19","price":"و به کوه‌ها [نمی‌نگرند] که چگونه [محکم بر زمین] نصب شده است؟","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5986,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:20","price":"و به زمین [نمی‌نگرند] که چگونه گسترده شده است؟","arabic":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5987,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:21","price":"[ای پیامبر،] پند بده، که تو فقط پنددهنده‌ای.","arabic":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5988,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:22","price":"تو بر آنان مسلط [و چیره] نیستی [که آنان را بر ایمان‌آوردن وادار کنی].","arabic":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5989,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:23","price":"اما کسی‌ که روی بگردانَد و کافر شود","arabic":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5990,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:24","price":"الله او را با بزرگ‌ترین عذاب، مجازات می‌کند.","arabic":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5991,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:25","price":"همانا بازگشت آنها به سوی ماست.","arabic":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5992,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"},{"name":"88:26","price":"سپس بی‌گمان، حسابشان [نیز] با ماست.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","category":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah"],"ayahNumber":5993,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fa"}],"chapter":["88 (Al-Ghashiyah)","Al-Ghashiyah","Surah Al-Ghashiyah","Chapter Al-Ghashiyah","Ghashiyah","Surah Ghashiyah","Chapter Ghashiyah","Al Ghashiyah","Surah Al Ghashiyah","Chapter Al Ghashiyah","Surah 88","Chapter 88","The Overwhelming Event","الغاشية"]}